---
gg_sMee
---

gg_sMee is a map for gungame servers (doh)

---
The map got:
- Custom dev textures.
- 20 spawns for each team.

- The red and blue boxes that have custom dev textures, shows u which side u on the map. ( Red = T, Blue = CT)
- There is no way to get outside the map (usefull for low gravity servers) 

Prefabs:
- I use the palmtree of MoHaX.

Textures:
- I use Youme Blue and red custom dev textures.
- I use Zaoman other custom dev textures.
---

I use Pakrat to show the custom textures so they wont be black and purple ingame.
This map is sponsord by A$. Azzshot.org.ru clan.

Also if u want to decompile this map, u need first my permission to do that!
want to contact me? go to azzshot.org.ru or add me on steam: Mvbommel

Dont critic on the pictures! first test ingame than give a assessment.
